title: cafter

content: I found this while researching about orderbooks ,  he is a kid in 9th or 10th and mastered blockchain and made some apps for cryptoand own 50cr worth of crypto .watch his channel : https://www.youtube.com/@GajeshSNaik/videosi am getting so jealous of him, i am a college student and he is just a kid but knows more them me,is it fine to get jealous ? are your also jealous of him? indian but.....

comments.author: pakhitheboss
comments.body: I just checked his YouTube and GitHub profile. This guy has a lot of contribution to many crypto projects but lacks the skills to be a good YouTube podcaster. The problem is not with his content the problem is the way he speaks. I was not able to understand because of his fake accent. Some of his questions were not making any sense. A good software engineer doesn't mean a good Youtuber. This is what I felt after watching his channel.

comments.author: elevates
comments.body: Please work on some good topics if you want to get merits and rankup. Such topics would not get you anywhere. Give some time to find topics that suits the current Indian Crypto situation. Investigate and then put it on this forum as topic with an interesting heading. None of us are bothered what anyone is earning. We are only concerned what we can earn and make a difference to this board.
